hopobject.body: How do you spell that? vitaros side effects The politician from Patna may have many achievements trailing him, the biggest of which is the rags to power high-jump — from a student leader in the Patna University to serving two terms as Bihar chief minister and finally a cabinet minister in charge of Railways in UPA 1. He may also have an equal number of disasters behind him, the pinnacle of which is the fodder scam for which he has now been convicted.
